"{\"uid\": \"independent.ie-irish-news-team-ireland-wins-bronze-in-international-culinary-olympics-competition-a530098896.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Junior Team Ireland with their bronze medals including Dubliner Chris Leech (fifth from left) Team Ireland took home a bronze medal at the Culinary Olympics in Germany after battling it out against 66 other nations.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999988090167, \"rank\": 1.1903350709921676e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.995995583111265, \"rank\": 0.002672570634556539, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Junior Team Ireland\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 19}, {\"ngram\": \"their bronze medals\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"Dubliner Chris Leech\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Culinary Olympics\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 156}, {\"ngram\": \"66 other nations\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 1,800 chefs took part in the international showcase event in Stuttgart this month, cooking a full three-course meal for 75 people in the junior category and 110 in the senior category.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"score\": 0.9999702936990157, \"rank\": 2.5969686865179966e-05, \"text\": \"Stuttgart\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Over 1,800 chefs\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 244}, {\"ngram\": \"the international showcase event\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"a full three-course meal\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"75 people\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the junior category\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"the senior category\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Ireland junior captain Chris Leech (24), who is from the village of Naul in north County Dublin described the win as a \\\"phenomenal achievement for a small nation\\\".\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999988090167, \"rank\": 1.1903350709921676e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naul,_Dublin\", \"score\": 0.8259079200079165, \"rank\": 0.17582417582416687, \"text\": \"Naul\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naul,_Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naul,_Dublin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"north County Dublin\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"phenomenal achievement\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"a small nation\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are over the moon.\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moon\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It really shows that hard work pays off.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We only signed up eight months ago and had a small budget unlike many of the bigger nations,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small budget\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the bigger nations\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Leech is a sous chef for catering company Sodexo.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Leech\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"a sous chef\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following in his father's career path, Mr Leech started off with a catering company while in transition year, and worked his way up through culinary school and worked under world renowned chef Raymond Blanc in the UK.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Raymond Blanc\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\"}, {\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999982354399543, \"rank\": 1.7599004821289048e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his father's career path\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Leech\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"a catering company\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"transition year\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"culinary school\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was thrown into the deep end from the start.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the deep end\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really green while working for him and just soaked up everything like a sponge, writing everything down,\\\" he told theIrish Independent.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999972319529, \"rank\": 2.6867407416543217e-09, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"a sponge\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After getting the call from the panel of chefs of Ireland, who chose the team through a combination of assessments, Mr Leech travelled to Limerick each week where the team trained for the Culinary Olympics.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997009979749097, \"rank\": 0.0002990630245144608, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"ht