bruary 3-7, required teams to cook a full-three course from the 'Restaurant of Nations' menu with 70 plates going out, four of these being to unknown judges.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-three course\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'Restaurant\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"Nations' menu\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"70 plates\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"unknown judges\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams were graded based on their service, plates and overall taste, with the main grading going towards consistency.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teams\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"their service\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"plates\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"overall taste\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the main grading\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Leech said this year judges threw a \\\"curveball\\\" calling for a vegan starter for the very first time.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Leech\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"curveball\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"a vegan starter\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"the very first time\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The junior team delivered a confit butternut squash fondant with an avocado chilli mousse, a special cracker and pickles on top.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The junior team\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"a confit\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"an avocado chilli mousse\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"a special cracker\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"pickles\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the main course, they delivered pork fillets wrapped in a burnt leek powder, carrot pur\\u00e9e, roast carrots, a potato terrine, raised pork belly croquette, and a cabbage ball with streaky bacon and \\\"loads of butter\\\".\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main course\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"pork fillets\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"a burnt leek powder\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"carrot pur\\u00e9e\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"roast carrots\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"a potato terrine\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"pork belly croquette\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"a cabbage ball\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"streaky bacon\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"loads\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"butter\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams cooked in specially-fitted glass-walled kitchens with visitors scrutinising their every move.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teams\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"specially-fitted glass-walled kitchens\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"their every move\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Generally I do not work well in big groups.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big groups\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a little daunting when you would be focused and working away and all of a sudden you look up and 400 or 500 people are just staring at you,\\\" Mr Leech said.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little daunting\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"400 or 500 people\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Leech\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Ireland was made up of a senior panel and junior panel as well as two helpers, amounting to 24 people in total, with little to no fans present.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999988090167, \"rank\": 1.1903350709921676e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a senior panel\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"junior panel\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"two helpers\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"24 people\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"little to no fans\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They faced giants such as Sweden, South Korea and Canada who each brought four teams and close to 500 spectators.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.998559181452452, \"rank\": 0.0009506905570103032, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 2895, \"end\": 2906, \"title\